data.description: Beautifully Maintained, spacious Ranch Home, on an ex-large corner lot, seller just upgraded exterior of the home with Hardi-Board siding and newly painted. This home has 3 bedrooms and 2 baths, large master bedroom with walk-in Closet. This lovely home offers an oversized Great Room with a Stacked-Stone Fireplace. With a Living room or can be used as a flex Room. This home is about 6 miles from Truist Park Home of the Braves. This home has a detached 3 car garage, with finished area above the garage that can be used as an office. Fenced in backyard. The seller has allowed this home to be used for several Motion Picture Movies and is listed with the GFE. This Home is Being Sold in its AS IS condition.
